{"tid":1243760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★行會通過公務員加薪　高級加4.75%中低級5.26%","createTime":"2019-06-19T15:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T07:28:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58ef5c74e113f9ac35cbaec7fb7cc30641f46598","tid":1243760,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局今日(19日)公布，行政長官會同行政會議已通過2019/20年度公務員薪酬調整方案，高層薪金級別及首長級的公務員加薪4.75%，中級及低級薪金級別的公務員，加薪幅度睇齊為5.26%。<br />\n<br />\n薪酬調整方案的生效日期追溯至今年4月1日，政府指會盡快將建議提交到立法會財務委員會考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190619/bkn-20190619180115592-0619_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190619%2Fbkn-20190619180115592-0619_00822_001.html&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=c0545879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190619/bkn-20190619180115592-0619_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"781d662ef2b10b00c8d33b386de0aa709322fa36","tid":1243760,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1564c09628f15ef754d33282e45edddbb77f4b9","tid":1243760,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"781d662ef2b10b00c8d33b386de0aa709322fa36","tid":1243760,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"你自稱低級公務員，有冇得加"},{"pid":"2573aa6cc856eb1032f8b96ff74fd9d8170e4ff2","tid":1243760,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11c04